title: Land of the Dead Road To Fiddler's Green + 1.1 patch
description:
Land of the Dead: Road to Fiddler&#039;s Green 1.0
Includes 1.1 patch

Install game, then install patch.

Visit undeadgames.com&#039;s forums for the latest info on mods and maps and other things for the game.

Decent FPS, not great, but has some fantastic zombie models.  And the second/third levels in single player will probably scare the crap out of you!  Also fun in Multiplayer Invasion mode!
